note top of DashiSpine
Strongest current evidence:
formal geometric/closure structure.
Closest to spacetime-formalism language,
not yet to full atom-by-atom physics.
end note

note top of TruthOpen
Programmer rule:
red items are not TODO comments to hand-wave.
They need named modules, fields, and checks
before diagrams should recolor them.
end note

note top of CoreSpineMetric
CoreSpine explains why several lanes
share the same ternary carrier vocabulary.
It is a typed bridge and diagrammatic interpretation layer,
not a solved unification theorem.
Concrete contraction still needs a certificate.
end note

note right of GapContinuum
This is where the public story needed correction:
not solved, no longer "missing from zero",
and now blocked on named seam hypotheses rather than vague future work.
end note

note bottom of DashiEmpirical
Closest current contact with experimental reality:
photonuclear / collider measurement organization.
This is useful, but it is not the same as deriving QCD,
and it is not the only atom/nuclear-facing surface.
Current empirical adequacy is not closed:
chi2 and orbit-shell surfaces do not yet prove
fixed-point prediction of observations.
end note

note bottom of DashiBoundaryExamples
Safe music bridge:
Z12 ~= Z3 x Z4 by CRT.
MusicalAttractor target:
K_music projects to a chosen diatonic scale,
L_music is chromatic dissonance, and descent is one-step.
Do not claim the perfect fifth shift gives a Z3 orbit;
+7 mod 12 has order 12.
end note

